<p><a name="Sample_budget" id="Sample_budget"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Personal_budget&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Sample budget">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Sample budget</span></h2>
